      • computePlanningMaxProgress

        int computePlanningMaxProgress(PCMMElement element,
                               PCMMMode mode)
                        throws CredibilityException
        Compute the maximum planning progress by PCMM element depending of the PCMM*mode:**PCMMMode.DEFAULT:in this mode we search the planning questions and fields*for each subelement.**PCMMMode.SIMPLIFIED:in this mode we just search the planning questions and* fields at the element level.**
        Parameters:
        element - the PCMM element to compute progress for*
        mode - the PCMM mode*@return the planning progress*@throws CredibilityException if an error occurs
        Returns:
        the PCMM planning max progress
        Throws:
        CredibilityException - if an error occurs

      • computePlanningProgress

        int computePlanningProgress(PCMMElement element,
                            Tag selectedTag,
                            PCMMMode mode)
                     throws CredibilityException
        Compute the planning progress by PCMM element depending of the PCMM mode: PCMMMode.DEFAULT: in this mode we search the planning answers for each subelement. PCMMMode.SIMPLIFIED: in this mode we just search the planning answers at the element level.
        Parameters:
        element - the PCMM element to compute progress for
        selectedTag - the current tag
        mode - the PCMM mode
        Returns:
        the planning progress
        Throws:
        CredibilityException - if an error occurs
